Package: valr
Type: Package
Title: Genome Interval Arithmetic in R
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(person('Jay', 'Hesselberth', role = c('aut', 'cre'), 
                    email = 'jay.hesselberth@gmail.com'),
             person('Kent', 'Riemondy', role = c('aut'),
                    email = 'kent.riemondy@ucdenver.edu'),
             person('Ryan', 'Sheridan', role = c('ctb'),
                    email = 'ryan.sheridan@ucdenver.edu'))
Description: Read and manipulate genome intervals and signals. valr 
             provides functionality similar to BEDtools and bedops within R,
             enabling interactive analysis and visualization of genome-scale data. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
